==English==
===Pronunciation===
*dout, /daʊt/, /<tt>daUt</tt>/
*:[[Rhymes:English:-aʊt|Rhymes: -aʊt]]
*{{audio|en-us-doubt.ogg|Audio (US)}}

=== Verb ===
'''to doubt''' ([[doubts]], [[doubted]], [[doubting]])
# To lack confidence in; to [[disbelieve]], [[question]], or [[suspect]].
#:''He '''doubt''' that was really what you meant.''

